### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### Check cache by md5
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cache/check?md5=d41d8cd98f00b204e9800998ecf8427e

### Upload image (enqueue for async processing)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/images/upload?enqueue=true
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

### Classify single image
GET http://localhost:8080/api/classify/one?imageId=1

### List categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories
